description: Bassist Christian McBride talks about his big band as well as about his smaller group, Inside Straight. This In Person with JazzTimes interview took place at the 2012 Newport Jazz Festival, where McBride performed with his group Inside Straight. Interview by Lee Mergner. Video by Melissa Mergner. Audio by Jen Kim.  Special thanks to Carolyn McClair, Melanie Nanez, Dan Melnick, Deborah Ross and the staff of George Wein Productions.
